{"tid":2320881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE《2020 MAMA》表演觀看數已破 700 萬　新歌〈Cry For Me〉下週發行！","createTime":"2020-12-11T06:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T09:00:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3da1fa700715d6ff17532ddc62581092f429beb3","tid":2320881,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_ef8583e816f43723a12c1161084eb302/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132253-888530.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_ef8583e816f43723a12c1161084eb302%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132253-888530.png&h=fbf3ac5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上週 TWICE 在《2020 MAMA》上帶來令人驚喜的新歌 &ldquo;Cry For Me&rdquo;，接下來她們也將正式推出音源給 ONCE 收藏！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 今天（11 日）宣布 TWICE 將於 18 日正式發行 &ldquo;Cry For Me&rdquo; 的音源，並公開了首波預告畫報。從下週一開始，TWICE 也將陸續釋出這首新歌的概念照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_07e8621d5b07b4bf9579f8660540272c/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-11/132253-888529.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_07e8621d5b07b4bf9579f8660540272c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-11%2F132253-888529.jpeg&h=b52dbc47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上週日 TWICE 在《2020 MAMA》的舞台上不僅帶來最新主打歌 &ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo;，還帶來 &ldquo;Cry For Me&rdquo; 這首充滿成熟魅力的新歌，而成員們融入演技詮釋的表演一曝光就掀起熱烈討論！<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Cry For Me&rdquo; 描寫擺盪在愛情與憎恨間的混亂感情，是 TWICE 出道以來從未嘗試過的風格，ONCE 們下週別忘了鎖定各種預告囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"66a059c1e407a4c5f7b1e65312032ba2c09bda86","tid":2320881,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:50:56.000Z","msg":"巧巧天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b